er, does not take into account the listener's feelings. One can still be honest and direct about feelings but express them in a way that doesn't offend or hurt. By practicing some of the suggestions listed above, you will be stretching and exercising your
 ability to communicate in a more caring and trusting manner. After a while it will become more automatic.
