he wanted a divorce. Later as he wrote a Love Letter he realized he was really afraid of being left or abandoned. He remembered how he felt as a child when his parents fought. He wrote a letter to his parents, and suddenly he felt loving toward his wife a
gain.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f29\fs32\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 
