\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 Repeatedly I have counseled couples who have been married for over twenty years. Their children have grown up and
