\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 Another example of the delayed reaction occurs on a social level. In sociology it is called the crisis of rising expectations. 
