gs onto our partner. If we did not feel safe to express our feelings to our parents or a past partner, all of a sudden we cannot get in touch with our feelings in the presence of our }{\b\i\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 present }{
\b\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 partner. At this point, no matter how supportive your partner is, when you are with your partner you will not feel safe. Feelings will be blocked.
