\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 When our unresolved feelings are being projected on our intimate partner, he or she is powerless to help us. All our partner can do is e
