ongoing changing seasons of love.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tqr\tx5986\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 THE SEASONS OF LOVE
