\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tqr\tx5986\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 A relationship is like a garden. If it is to thrive it must be watered regularly. Special care must he given, taking into account the sea\-
 sons as well as any unpredictable weather. New seeds must be sown
\par and weeds must be pulled. Similarly; to keep the magic of love alive we must understand its seasons and nurture love's special needs.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tqr\tx5986\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f28\fs22\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 
